room_title: Escape room "Inventor's Basement" by Escape Rooms Unlocked in Sarasota
room_description:
The famous Dr. Ima Smarty has discovered the secrets of time travel. But with her invention comes great danger. As she visited places in the past to test her machine, she was actually altering time. Can you and your fellow agents at the Time Travel Bureau break into her basement laboratory and set time right?
You only have 60 minutes before the machine shuts down forever and life as we know it is forever changed. Can you save time before the clock runs out?
